{"tid":2274148,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★Apple股東集體起訴Tim Cook 隱瞞不利消息","createTime":"2020-11-06T08:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T08:54:09.000Z","uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fd745638d8eaf4255421562dda5188f09472c2b4","tid":2274148,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:46:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hbyWHER.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhbyWHER.png&h=1f05c4a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外媒報道，蘋果公司(Apple Inc.)面臨股東的集體訴訟，主要指控行政總裁庫克隱瞞中國對iPhone需求下降的消息，從而導致投資者損失數十億美元。<br />\n<br />\n據報，美國地區法官批准由英國養老基金牽頭的集體訴訟，事緣於2018年11月1日庫克向分析員表示，Apple在新興市場正面臨銷售壓力，但中國並不包括在內。不過，在2019年1月2日，Apple意外將季度收入預測下調，庫克將此歸咎於中美貿易緊張對中國經濟造成的壓力。當時事件導致Apple股價於第二日下跌10%，市值更蒸發740億美元。不過，其後Apple及庫克均表示，沒有證據表明他們意圖欺騙股東。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20201106/bkn-20201106124843876-1106_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20201106%2Fbkn-20201106124843876-1106_00842_001.html&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9iBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=2a098292\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20201106/bkn-20201106124843876-1106_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"dcbc45e5f81f8e34ed33209ed23212c52d7b442e","tid":2274148,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf0de5df4f04a5eb518b26033080af74efa8594","tid":2274148,"uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dcbc45e5f81f8e34ed33209ed23212c52d7b442e","tid":2274148,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T0